trans-unit.source: Enables the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebScriptEnablingBehavior" /> for an endpoint through configuration.
trans-unit.target: Habilita <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebScriptEnablingBehavior" /> para un extremo a través de la configuración.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebScriptEnablingElement> is a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.BehaviorExtensionElement> subtype that can be used to include the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebScriptEnablingBehavior> on an endpoint through configuration.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebScriptEnablingElement> es un subtipo <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.BehaviorExtensionElement> que se puede utilizar para incluir <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebScriptEnablingBehavior> en un extremo a través de la configuración.

trans-unit.source: There are no configurable properties on this element.
trans-unit.target: No hay ninguna propiedad configurable en este elemento.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebScriptEnablingBehavior>, in turn, allows an endpoint to be accessed by ASP.NET AJAX Web pages when it is configured with the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebScriptEnablingBehavior>, a su vez, permite a las páginas web de AJAX de ASP.NET obtener acceso a un extremo cuando se configura con <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>.

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to enable a WCF service to respond to ASP.NET AJAX clients, see [Creating WCF Services for ASP.NET AJAX](~/docs/framework/wcf/feature-details/creating-wcf-services-for-aspnet-ajax.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información sobre cómo habilitar un servicio WCF para responder a los clientes de AJAX de ASP.NET, vea [crear servicios de WCF para AJAX de ASP.NET](~/docs/framework/wcf/feature-details/creating-wcf-services-for-aspnet-ajax.md).
